@startuml
title Сценарий создания объявления (Happy Path)

actor Seller
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Listing Service" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Redis Cache" as Cache
participant "Notification Service" as Notify

Seller -> UI: Нажать "Разместить на модерации"
activate UI

UI -> API: POST /api/listings
activate API

API -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
API -> DB: Insert listing with status = 'PENDING_MODERATION', created_at = NOW()
activate DB
DB --> API: ListingID
deactivate DB

API -> DB: Link categories to ListingID
activate DB
DB --> API: OK
deactivate DB

API -> DB: COMMIT
note right: Транзакция завершена успешно

API -> Cache: Invalidate 'active_listings'
activate Cache
Cache --> API: OK
deactivate Cache

API -> Notify: Trigger notification (moderator_id, listing_id)
activate Notify
Notify --> API: Queued
deactivate Notify

API --> UI: 200 OK (Listing URL)
deactivate API

UI --> Seller: Показать объявление на модерации
deactivate UI

@enduml
